Project 1 
Two-Tier WebApp with Docker & Jenkins

- Automate the deployment pipeline
- Reduce the manual effort
- Automatically trigger build steps
- Deploy after tests pass

TechStack:
Frontend  - Flask, a lightweight Python web framework
Database - MySQL for storing & retrieving data
DevOps Tools - Github, Docker, Docker Compose & Jenkins
Environment - AWS, specifically on EC2 server

Steps:
- Set up EC2, install services
- Connect Jenkins to Github repository
- Jenkins build image on push
- Docker compose spin up ocntainers
- Jenkins runs integration tests
- Access app on port 5000

Potential Problems
Your Jenkins build might fail multiple times due to permission issues or communication error.

