#Project 4

Deploying a Prometheus Observability Stack

Core Objectives
- Deploy complete monitoring stack
- Understand the tool integration
- Detect application slowness, throughput

Cloud Provider - Azure

Core Tools - Prometheus, Grafana & Alert Manager

Deployment Tools - Terraform for kubernetes cluster & Helm to deploy the monitoring tools

Steps
- Deploy kubernetes with Terraform
- Use Helm to deploy tools
- Configure Pormetheus to scrape targets
- Set up Grafana dashboard
- Run load tests on application
- Trigger and verify alerts

Time Investment
Comparatively longer for beginners

Potential Problems
High chance you might go over your free cloud credits with this project

