#Project 5
AI-Assisted DevOps (AIOps)

Core Objectives
- Automate DevOps workflows with AI
- Help with incident responses
- Provide operational recommendations

Tech Stack
Models  -  Python, LLMs via Hugging Face or OpenAI APIs
DevOps Tools  - CI/CD pipeline, Alert Manager, Chatbot
Validation  -  Grafana dashboards

Steps
- Alert manager notifies AI agent
- Agent interprets logs, suggests steps
- Agent can restart pods/deployments
- Use Grafana for human validation

Potential Problems
This project is not as easy as you think & required a human in the loop for validation
because you cannot fully trust the AI system

